parsed_question.rephrased_question: What are the most common yellow NYC taxi pickups?
key_points: Yellow taxis account for more drop-offs in Brooklyn than green taxis, but their pickup numbers have decreased since the introduction of green boro taxis.
Manhattan still has the largest number of taxi pickups, with around 85% of all NYC taxi pickups occurring there.
